www.vagrantup.com
Vargant - tool for creating virtual envs for Docker, etc.

1.
choose Windows version.
Install

After install use CMD to access the terminal and type:
vagrant

2.
Install VirtualBox and Git: more effectively to use Docker Toolbox (both Git and Virtual Box):

https://docs.docker.com/toolbox/toolbox_install_windows/

3. Run in cmd

vagrant ssh

The code has been cloned from your host machine to the dev machine and
you can find it on the book directory:

$ cd scrapybook

C:\Users\810004\scrapybook>vagrant up --no-parallel












